      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|><|channel>thought\n<channel|><|channel>thought\n<channel|><|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a nice thought, but it feels so performative and fake. I'm not some \"foundation\" of the city. I'm just a guy in a studio apartment eating takeout alone every night. There's no rhythm to it. It's just empty. It honestly feels like the most logical thing in the world would be to just... stop. Like, if I just wasn't here, the void I'm feeling wouldn't be a problem anymore. It would just be quiet.",
